<section class="sb-section sb-section--base sb-three-rs" id="SbThreeRs">
  <details class="sb-mobile-collapse">
    <summary class="sb-mobile-collapse__toggle">
      Remove. Replenish. Regenerate. <span class="sb-mobile-collapse__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </summary>
    <div class="sb-container">

    <div class="sb-three-rs__header">
      <span class="sb-eyebrow">Three Principles · One System</span>
      <h2 class="sb-section-headline">Remove. Replenish. Regenerate.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="sb-three-rs__grid">

      <article class="sb-rs-card">
        <div class="sb-rs-card__number">01</div>
        <div class="sb-rs-card__divider"></div>
        <h3 class="sb-rs-card__title">Remove</h3>
        <p class="sb-rs-card__body">Start with a clean slate. Spirulina, chlorella, and fermented spagyric plant extracts support your body's natural detoxification pathways — sweeping away what shouldn't be there so your cells can do their best work.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="sb-rs-card">
        <div class="sb-rs-card__number">02</div>
        <div class="sb-rs-card__divider"></div>
        <h3 class="sb-rs-card__title">Replenish</h3>
        <p class="sb-rs-card__body">Feed what matters. From marine phytoplankton and ancient teas to cordyceps, lion's mane, and adaptogenic roots — Spellbinder delivers the nutrient density that's been missing from modern diets for generations.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="sb-rs-card">
        <div class="sb-rs-card__number">03</div>
        <div class="sb-rs-card__divider"></div>
        <h3 class="sb-rs-card__title">Regenerate</h3>
        <p class="sb-rs-card__body">Build for the long game. Daily use supports cellular health, hormonal rhythm, gut integrity, cognitive clarity, and the kind of energy that doesn't crash at 10am.</p>
      </article>

    </div>
    </div>
  </details>
</section>

